 for longwave MRT estimation while evaluating the\nradiant temperature distribution and radiant asymmetry of spaces.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Jul 2022 02:54:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Jul 2022 01:46:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-27"}
