rison with the case of the\nGaussian distribution. Additionally, we also discuss a mechanism of primordial\nblack holes formation for this upward step inflation model by trapping the\ninflaton in the bottom of the step.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Jul 2022 05:26:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 3 Aug 2022 10:11:41 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 30 Dec 2022 12:29:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-02"}
