 charge inhomogeneity implies an enhancement of the counterion\ndensity at the contact with the charged line and a diminution of the pressure\nbetween two parallel lines in comparison with the uniformly charged ones (with\nthe same mean charge densities).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Jul 2022 12:59:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-26"}
